latestPosts.caption:
It’s the element of surprise & chance encounters - those that seem like sheer luck on the surface that make life magical. But in reality, the shift often happens underground, inward, invisible to the naked eye. It’s only the first leaf that you see grow, the first blooming flower you cherish, or the first fruit that ripens sweet enough to taste that we experience the beautiful act of nature. 

All of it - possible purely because we sowed the seeds with love, watered everyday (almost?) & just believed it will happen. Because, well - it’s nature. Why would it not?

Thank you @elleindia @kubbrasait @trupalpandya for making this happen ♥️

Thank you @krishadedhia13 for literally being on all fours to help pull this off 💜

Thank you @onitsukatigerindia @lapaz.in @gateway.pr @elsanilajofficial @dujaindia @litmusindia @shopagape.in @antarez.jewels @radhikaagrawalstudio for the amazing work you do that allow us stylists to create 💕
